Package InfrastructureManager.Modules.Scenario

Class ScenarioModuleObject

java.lang.Object
InfrastructureManager.PlatformObject
InfrastructureManager.Modules.Scenario.ScenarioModuleObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Scenario, ScenarioDispatcher, ScenarioEditor
public class ScenarioModuleObject
extends PlatformObject
Concrete implementation of PlatformObject for the Scenario Module.

All objects (input and outputs included) of the module must extend this class.

Additionally to access to the owner module's pointer and the built-in logger, this particular class enables objects inside the Scenario Module to have access to the shared resource that is the Scenario defined for the module.
